sub_title: Certified Coach ACC ICF | Relocation Coordinator | English for Coaches Trainer & Curriculum Developer
summary:
Relocation Coordinator, Certified Coach ACC ICF and English for Coaches Trainer with personalized and individually tailored approach in everything I do.

Relocation assistance: with double own experience of being an expat, I help navigate big changes smoothly & comfortably, both for companies & expats, I provide both informational & emotional support & help to understand cultural differences better & to make them work together.

Coach profile: Certified ACC ICF Coach with 300+ hours experience as a Life and Executive Coach for individuals, groups and teams. Among my clients have been: expats, refugees, business owners, career relaunchers, start-ups, executives, representatives of creative and IT professions from all over the world, so cross-cultural coaching is a big part of my practice.

Other work experience: 15+ years in Leadership and other roles, in Change management, IT, Education, Medical Equipment and Non-profit.

As a volunteer I've been involved in: Building teams, Relocation assistance, Marketing, Organizing big and small events, Leading several projects simultaneously, Creation and successful delegation of a non-profit organization and various projects.

Personal development is a very important part of my life and career. I'm constantly growing and help my clients find their best ways to and in their new life.

Interested in working with me?
Feel free to send me a message.
